      <num>SEC. 2.11</num>
      <heading>Public library established.*</heading>
      <content>
        <p>A public library is hereby established in and for the city.</p>
        <p>(Code 1938, Sec. 240.)</p>
        <p>* For state law authorizing the establishment of a public library, see Ed. C. A.,
               Sec. 22201.</p>
      </content>
